Solve Linear Set of Equations
\[
\begin{bmatrix}
R_1 + R_2 & -R_2 & 0 \\
-R_2 & R_2 + R_3 + R_4 & -R_4 \\
0 & -R_4 & R_4 + R_5 + R_6
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
i_1 \\
i_2 \\
i_3
\end{bmatrix}
=
\begin{bmatrix}
v_s \\
0 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\]







Looks like Ohm’s Law!


